  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-02-27",
    "date": "2025-07-10T15:28:01Z",
    "text": "This bill directs the Department of Homeland Security to designate Haiti for temporary protected status (TPS) for 18 months beginning August 3, 2025. (Eligible nationals\u00a0of a TPS-designated country\u00a0may obtain employment authorization, may not be detained on the basis of their immigration status, and are not subject to removal while they retain TPS.)"
  },
